    Stores the result of a computation and provides utility methods to manipulate it.

    This class stores the raw result of a given computation, and can be initialized with additional information representing the execution time, and the Exception thrown by the computation.

    RuntimeActionResult provides an isError() method that returns true if it contains an Exception. This allows to quickly check whether the underlying computation succeeded or failed.
